<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar, Greater Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 54, 60<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar or Greater Familiar <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>   with inherent see-invis</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> dies when owner uses Invisibility or Invisibility to Undead.  No only is this not as intended but it open us up to griefing by players pretending they want an evac to EJ, grouping with us, and invising us.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a level 54 or 60 familiar and cast Invisibility or Invisibility to Undead on yourself<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Minor Familiar, Lesser Familiar, Familiar, Greater Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 29, 49, 54, 60<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar dies when the owner Absconds/Evacuates.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a familiar and cast Abscond/Evacuate.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Minor Familiar, Lesser Familiar, Familiar, Greater Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 29, 49, 54, 60<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar dies when the owner has Call of the Hero cast on him.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a familiar and have a magician cast Call of the Hero on you.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Minor Familiar, Lesser Familiar, Familiar, Greater Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 29, 49, 54, 60<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar dies when the owner's Eye of Zomm is killed, causes mana/health losses to owner.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a familiar, summon an Eye of Zomm, kill the Eye of Zomm.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Minor Familiar, Lesser Familiar, Familiar, Greater Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 29, 49, 54, 60<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Familiar dies when the owner casts the invisible Eye of Tallon.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a familiar, summon an Eye of Tallon.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Ability</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Improved Familiar<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: n/a<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with Ability</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Does not include the mana regen increase, effective casting level increase, or mana pool increase that it is supposed to.  Only includes resists.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Summon a Greater Familiar, time med from oom to fom.  Summon an Improved Familiar, time med from oom to fom.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Eye of Tallon<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Spell level</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: 58<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Problem with spell</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Eye of Tallon poofs early if the random-style invis component wears off.  Invis component should not be random.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   How bug can be replicated</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Repeatedly summoning an Eye of Tallon should produce at least one which has a short-duration invis.<br>
